questions.question: Oil, natural gas and coal are examples of
Which of the following is an example of genetic engineering?
questions.answer1: Inserting a gene into plants that makes them resistant to insects
questions.answer2: Growing a whole plant from a single cell
questions.answer3: Attaching the root of one type of plant to the stem of another type of plant
questions.answer4: Finding the sequences of bases in plant DNA
questions.correctAnswer: Finding the sequences of bases in plant DNA

questions.question: What is the main cause of seasons on the Earth?
questions.answer1: The tilt of the Earth's axis in relation to the sun
questions.answer2: The speed that the Earth rotates around the sun
questions.answer3: Changes in the amount of energy coming from the sun
questions.answer4: The distance between the Earth and the sun
questions.correctAnswer: Changes in the amount of energy coming from the sun
